---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/Main.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="Build: Our Systems">

    <!-- PAGE HERO -->
    <section class="relative bg-linear-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-indigo-800 text-white py-24 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-24 -right-24 w-96 h-96 bg-purple-500 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-16 -left-16 w-72 h-72 bg-indigo-400 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <p class="text-indigo-300 font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">System Architecture</p>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-5 leading-tight">How We Built It</h1>
            <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-indigo-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Three integrated subsystems working in harmony: community scalability, gravity-based irrigation, and sustainable water management.
            </p>
        </div>
        <!-- Wave bottom -->
        <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 80" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                <path d="M0 80L48 72C96 64 192 48 288 44C384 40 480 48 576 52C672 56 768 56 864 52C960 48 1056 40 1152 40C1248 40 1344 48 1392 52L1440 56V80H1392C1344 80 1248 80 1152 80C1056 80 960 80 864 80C768 80 672 80 576 80C480 80 384 80 288 80C192 80 96 80 48 80H0Z" fill="#030712"/>
            </svg>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ===================== SECTION 1 ===================== -->

    <!-- 1C — Title Banner -->
    <section class="bg-gray-950 pt-24 pb-10 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-blue-500/40"></div>
                <div class="shrink-0 bg-gray-900 border border-blue-500/40 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 text-center shadow-lg shadow-blue-900/20">
                    <p class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Subsystem 01</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
                        Community Scalability
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-blue-500/40"></div>
            </div>
            <!-- Arrow down -->
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
                <svg class="w-6 h-10 text-blue-400 animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 1B + 1A — Description + Image -->
    <section class="bg-gray-950 py-16 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

                <!-- 1B: Description -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-950/50 border border-blue-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-400"></div>
                        <span class="text-blue-300 text-sm font-mono">subsystem_01.description</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white leading-snug">
                        Scalable Community Infrastructural Systems
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        This subsystem enables the expansion of modular, mechanically-driven greenhouses across communities by establishing a repeatable, low-cost infrastructure model that does not rely on external power systems like solar. Each greenhouse integrates water collection, storage, and distribution systems to sustainably support crop growth, making them highly adaptable to different environments. By partnering directly with local food pantries, the system creates localized food production hubs that reduce dependency on external supply chains.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        Through targeted advocacy and collaboration with local governments, our nonprofit secures funding to deploy these systems at scale, allowing for continuous replication from one community to the next. This approach ensures long-term sustainability, food security, and equitable access to fresh produce.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        <!-- (PLACEHOLDER BULLET POINTS — key facts/specs) -->
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Modular, replicable greenhouse design for rapid deployment</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Integrated water collection and gravity-fed irrigation systems</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-blue-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Government-funded expansion model supporting community-to-community scaling</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- 1A: Image -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500/30 to-indigo-500/30 rounded-2xl blur-sm"></div>
                    <div class="relative bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                        <img src="/images/First.png" alt="Description" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-600 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">(PLACEHOLDER IMAGE)</p> <!-- I will work on this later(Abhi, give me the photo I asked -->
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1">Replace with &lt;img&gt; tag pointing to your photo</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Wavy Divider 1→2 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-950 overflow-hidden leading-none">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
            <path d="M0 30 C180 55 360 5 540 30 C720 55 900 5 1080 30 C1260 55 1380 15 1440 30 L1440 60 L0 60 Z" fill="#111827"/>
        </svg>
    </div>


    <!-- ===================== SECTION 2 ===================== -->

    <!-- 2C — Title Banner -->
    <section class="bg-gray-900 pt-20 pb-10 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-purple-500/40"></div>
                <div class="shrink-0 bg-gray-950 border border-purple-500/40 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 text-center shadow-lg shadow-purple-900/20">
                    <p class="text-purple-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Subsystem 02</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
                        Gravity-based Irrigation System
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-purple-500/40"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
                <svg class="w-6 h-10 text-purple-400 animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 2B + 2A — Description + Image (image LEFT, text RIGHT for variety) -->
    <section class="bg-gray-900 py-16 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

                <!-- 2A: Image (left on desktop) -->
                <div class="relative order-2 lg:order-1">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500/30 to-pink-500/30 rounded-2xl blur-sm"></div>
                    <div class="relative bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                        <img src="/images/Second.png" alt="Description" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-600 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">(PLACEHOLDER IMAGE)</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1">Replace with &lt;img&gt; tag pointing to your photo</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- 2B: Description (right on desktop) -->
                <div class="space-y-6 order-1 lg:order-2">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-purple-950/50 border border-purple-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-purple-400"></div>
                        <span class="text-purple-300 text-sm font-mono">subsystem_02.description</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white leading-snug">
                        Passive Water Distribution Infrastructure
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        This subsystem delivers a fully mechanical, gravity-based irrigation system that eliminates the need for pumps or external power sources. Water is collected and stored in elevated tanks supported by ground-planted tripod structures, creating natural pressure that drives consistent, top-down distribution through a structured piping network. This ensures efficient and reliable irrigation across the entire greenhouse while minimizing energy requirements and system complexity.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        By leveraging elevation and controlled flow, the system reduces operational costs and increases long-term durability, making it ideal for scalable deployment in resource-limited communities. Its simplicity allows for easy replication, maintenance, and adaptation across different greenhouse configurations.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Elevated water storage enabling gravity-fed irrigation</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Even, top-down distribution through PVC lattice piping system</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Zero-energy operation with minimal maintenance requirements</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Wavy Divider 2→3 -->
    <div class="bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden leading-none">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 1440 60" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-full">
            <path d="M0 30 C180 55 360 5 540 30 C720 55 900 5 1080 30 C1260 55 1380 15 1440 30 L1440 60 L0 60 Z" fill="#030712"/>
        </svg>
    </div>


    <!-- ===================== SECTION 3 ===================== -->

    <!-- 3C — Title Banner -->
    <section class="bg-gray-950 pt-20 pb-10 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent to-green-500/40"></div>
                <div class="shrink-0 bg-gray-900 border border-green-500/40 rounded-xl px-8 py-4 text-center shadow-lg shadow-green-900/20">
                    <p class="text-green-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">Subsystem 03</p>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white">
                        Sustainable Environmental Management
                    </h2>
                </div>
                <div class="h-px flex-1 bg-gradient-to-l from-transparent to-green-500/40"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center mt-8">
                <svg class="w-6 h-10 text-green-400 animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/>
                </svg>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3B + 3A — Description + Image -->
    <section class="bg-gray-950 py-16 reveal">
        <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">

                <!-- 3B: Description -->
                <div class="space-y-6">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-950/50 border border-green-800/50 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5">
                        <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400"></div>
                        <span class="text-green-300 text-sm font-mono">subsystem_03.description</span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold text-white leading-snug">
                        Closed-Loop Resource Optimization
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg leading-relaxed">
                        This subsystem ensures that each greenhouse operates as a self-sustaining environmental system by minimizing waste and continuously recycling key resources. Water is collected, stored, and redistributed through gravity-fed systems, while organic plant waste is repurposed into nutrient-rich fertilizer to support ongoing crop growth. This closed-loop approach reduces external inputs and maximizes efficiency within each greenhouse.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-gray-500 leading-relaxed">
                        By integrating natural cycles into the infrastructure, the system enhances long-term sustainability, lowers operational costs, and improves resilience in resource-limited communities. It creates a regenerative growing environment where outputs are continuously reinvested back into production.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-400 text-sm">
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Water collection and reuse through integrated storage and distribution</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Organic waste conversion into fertilizer for continuous soil enrichment</li>
                        <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-400 mt-0.5">▹</span> Closed-loop design reducing external resource dependency</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <!-- 3A: Image -->
                <div class="relative">
                    <div class="absolute -inset-1 bg-gradient-to-br from-green-500/30 to-cyan-500/30 rounded-2xl blur-sm"></div>
                    <div class="relative bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden aspect-video flex items-center justify-center">
                        <img src="/images/Third.png" alt="Description" class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
                            <svg class="w-16 h-16 text-gray-600 mx-auto mb-3" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 16l4.586-4.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L16 16m-2-2l1.586-1.586a2 2 0 012.828 0L20 14m-6-6h.01M6 20h12a2 2 0 002-2V6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">(PLACEHOLDER IMAGE)</p>
                            <p class="text-gray-600 text-xs mt-1">Replace with &lt;img&gt; tag pointing to your photo</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </section>


    <!-- ===================== BOTTOM CTA ===================== -->
    <section class="relative bg-linear-to-br from-indigo-600 via-purple-600 to-indigo-800 text-white py-20 overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -top-20 -right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-purple-400 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="relative max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-4">Want to Get Involved?</h2>
            <p class="text-indigo-100 text-lg mb-8">These systems are built by students, for communities. Reach out if you want to support, collaborate, or learn more.</p>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-white text-indigo-700 px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-bold hover:bg-indigo-50 active:scale-95 transition-all duration-150 shadow-lg">
                Contact Us
            </a>
        </div>
    </section>

</MainLayout>


<style>
    /* Initial hidden state for scroll-reveal elements */
    .reveal {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(2.5rem);
        transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
    }
    .reveal.visible {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }
</style>

<script>
    const observer = new IntersectionObserver(
        (entries) => {
            entries.forEach((entry) => {
                if (entry.isIntersecting) {
                    entry.target.classList.add('visible');
                    // Once visible, stop observing (no re-animation)
                    observer.unobserve(entry.target);
                }
            });
        },
        {
            threshold: 0.1,      // trigger when 10% of section is visible
            rootMargin: '0px 0px -60px 0px'  // slightly before it hits the very bottom
        }
    );

    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach((el) => observer.observe(el));
</script>
